Blue Moon
comments: There are 3 Ted FioRito takes in 1934: A & B on October 19th and C on November 19th. The latter was released on Blue Moon (1934). However, as there are no other recordings on November 19th, it's possible that the C-take is an engineer's remake (dub) of either takes A or B, rather than a new recording. If confirmed, this would make this take the original recording of Blue Moon .
